ent-MutationNearSightedness = Near Sightedness
    .desc = The holder of this mutation has poor eyesight.

ent-MutationBlindness = Blindness
    .desc = Renders the subject completely blind.

ent-MutationThermalVision = Thermal Vision
    .desc = The user of this genome can visually perceive the unique human thermal signature.

ent-MutationActionThermalVision = { ent-ToggleThermalVision }
    .desc = { ent-ToggleThermalVision.desc }

ent-MutationIlliterate = Illiterate
    .desc = Causes a severe case of Aphasia that prevents reading or writing.

ent-MutationLaserEyes = Laser Eyes
    .desc = Reflects concentrated light back from the eyes.

ent-MutationEnhancedPerception = Enhanced Perception
    .desc = Improves the subject's peripheral vision, letting them see things in the corner of their eyes better.

ent-MutationWeakPerception = Weak Perception
    .desc = The subject has almost no peripheral vision, only able to see almost directly infront of themselves.